        <abstract> 
<p>Sends WEG the two articles [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">11163</hi>] with references.</p> 
            <p>CD thinks savages do not have names for shades of colours, which is curious since those he has known have names for every slight promontory or hill.</p>
